OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782407919
OL,3,CDriver almost three times over speed
OL,4,Climit before causing death of teenage
OL,5,Cboy
OL,7,FA dangerous driver who was almost
OL,8,Fthree times over the speed limit
OL,9,Fbefore causing the death of a teenage
OL,10,Fboy in Kent has been jailed.
OL,12,FCameron Langley-McColm, of Coombe Road
OL,13,Fin Maidstone, was sentenced to seven-
OL,14,Fand-a-half years in jail after his
OL,15,Fwhite BMW Sport hit Kieran Byrne, who
OL,16,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene
OL,18,FOn the evening of 8 July 2023, Langley-
OL,19,FMcColm was along Heath Road in
OL,20,FCoxheath when his vehicle struck
OL,21,FKieran, who was riding an e-scooter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
