PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782407919
OL,3,CDriver almost three times over speed
OL,4,Climit before causing death of teenage
OL,5,Cboy
OL,7,FThe teenager was thrown 28 metres from
OL,8,Fthe point of impact.
OL,10,FOfficers attended, along with
OL,11,Fparamedics, but Kieran could not be
OL,12,Fsaved.
OL,14,FA second boy, who was 14 at the time,
OL,15,Fwas also clipped by the speeding car
OL,16,Fbut suffered no serious injuries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
