OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782407919
OL,3,CDriver almost three times over speed
OL,4,Climit before causing death of teenage
OL,5,Cboy
OL,7,FRoadside tests, including for
OL,8,Fintoxication and drug use, were
OL,9,Fconducted at the scene which Langley-
OL,10,FMcColm passed and he was released
OL,11,Funder investigation.
OL,13,FOn 16 July 2023, he attended a
OL,14,Fvoluntary interview where he claimed
OL,15,Fthe victim had swerved in front of his
OL,16,Fcar as he was trying to overtake him.
OL,18,FThrough CCTV footage and witness
OL,19,Fstatements, police identified that
OL,20,FLangley-McColm was speeding moments
OL,21,Fbefore the collision.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
