OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782407919
OL,3,CDriver almost three times over speed
OL,4,Climit before causing death of teenage
OL,5,Cboy
OL,7,FHe was driving at 82mph on the 30mph
OL,8,Froad and on the wrong side of the road.
OL,10,FThe investigation also proved that
OL,11,FKieran and the second boy had been
OL,12,Ftravelling on the right hand side of
OL,13,Fthe road before the collision and had
OL,14,Fnot swerved in front of the car, as
OL,15,FLangley-McColm claimed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
