FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782407919
OL,3,CDriver almost three times over speed
OL,4,Climit before causing death of teenage
OL,5,Cboy
OL,7,FOn 13 January 2026, Langley-McColm was
OL,8,Fcharged with causing death by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving. He was sentenced at
OL,10,FMaidstone Crown Court on Tuesday 16
OL,11,FJune, where he also received an 11
OL,12,Fyear driving ban.
OL,14,FDetective Constable David Holmes, from
OL,15,Fthe Serious Collision Investigation
OL,16,FUnit, said: "The death of Kieran Bryne
OL,17,Fwas tragic and completely avoidable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
