OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1782407919
OL,3,CDriver almost three times over speed
OL,4,Climit before causing death of teenage
OL,5,Cboy
OL,7,F"Cameron Langley-McColm was driving at
OL,8,Fmore than 82 mph in a 30mph and had no
OL,9,Fconsideration for other road users.
OL,10,FHis actions were reckless and
OL,11,Funnecessary.
OL,13,F"As a result, a young boy lost his
OL,14,Flife and a family has been left
OL,15,Fdevastated.
OL,17,F"Driving at speed increases the risk
OL,18,Fof death or serious injury and we will
OL,19,Fcontinue to crack down on motorists
OL,20,Fwho endanger others."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
